videos.description: Ben Simmons doesn't take a dribble and drops the pass right into Danny Green's hand for the transition dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Simmons throws touchdown pass to Green for dunk) 2021/05/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Simmons throws touchdown pass to Green for dunk

videos.description: Jaxson Hayes flushes home the putback dunk surrounded by defenders. Dwight Howard follows it up with an alley-oop slam.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Hayes, Howard exchange impressive dunks in the 2nd quarter) 2021/05/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hayes, Howard exchange impressive dunks in the 2nd quarter

videos.description: Joel Embiid goes right at Jaxson Hayes and converts the and-1. Then Ben Simmons cleanly picks Lonzo Ball's pocket and puts in the easy layup.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Embiid, Simmons overpower Pelicans in final minute of first half) 2021/05/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Embiid, Simmons overpower Pelicans in final minute of first half

videos.description: Joel Embiid shows off the range and drains a couple 3-pointers.
videos.headline: Embiid cashes in back-to-back 3's

videos.description: Kira Lewis Jr. knocks down the 3-pointer then gets the steal and jam giving New Orleans the lead heading into the fourth.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Lewis gives the Pelicans the lead with a 3 then a dunk) 2021/05/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lewis gives the Pelicans the lead with a 3 then a dunk

videos.description: The Pelicans and 76ers give the ball away multiple times as both teams struggle to hold onto the ball.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Cue circus music, Pelicans and 76ers have sloppy sequence) 2021/05/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cue circus music, Pelicans and 76ers have sloppy sequence

videos.description: Tobias Harris hits the 3 to give Philadelphia the lead. The 76ers, trying to run out the clock, get an eight-second violation, but the Pelicans turn it over to end the game.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (76ers survive Pelicans in late game drama) 2021/05/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: 76ers survive Pelicans in late-game drama
